# GAIA Official Reseller Guidelines

Welcome to the GAIA Partner Program. This document outlines all responsibilities, permissions, and procedures for authorized resellers of GAIA — the intelligent assistant platform.

---

## ✅ Authorized Usage

Resellers are granted a non-exclusive, revocable license to:

- Market, distribute, and sell GAIA software (desktop, mobile, web)
- Use GAIA's official branding and visual assets in promotions
- Offer white-labeled versions under special license (see below)

---

## 💼 Reseller Responsibilities

### 1. Activation & Licensing
- All customers must activate GAIA using the **official license key portal**
- Activation data (email, license key, timestamp) must be logged for compliance

### 2. Customer Support
- First-level support is the reseller’s responsibility
- GAIA Core Team handles escalated issues via **support@gaia-ai.io**

### 3. Updates & Maintenance
- Resellers will receive access to new versions via a secured dashboard
- All update deployments must be verified before distribution

---

